WEBVTT

00:49.640 --> 00:50.900
Mine is not bad either.

00:51.000 --> 00:52.000
Teacher, what about mine?

00:52.000 --> 00:53.400
Not bad for your first time.

00:53.400 --> 00:54.400
Thank you, Teacher.

00:54.400 --> 00:55.480
Teacher, look at mine.

00:55.480 --> 00:55.920
It's average.

00:55.920 --> 00:57.200
You did a great job on this.

00:57.200 --> 00:57.960
Teach me later.

00:57.960 --> 00:58.480
Right?

00:59.600 --> 01:01.280
How did you make this?

01:03.160 --> 01:03.760
It's okay.

01:04.120 --> 01:05.720
Teacher, what level is this?

01:07.240 --> 01:08.600
If this were in the past,

01:08.760 --> 01:10.360
this would get you beheaded.

01:11.480 --> 01:13.480
Are you complimenting me, Teacher?

01:13.840 --> 01:14.440
It's okay.

01:15.800 --> 01:16.880
Let me see.

01:18.880 --> 01:20.200
Xiaocen, this is not bad.

01:20.200 --> 01:21.660
It's a pleasant surprise.

01:21.880 --> 01:24.140
Smooth lines and exquisite use of color.

01:24.280 --> 01:24.800
Not bad.

01:25.480 --> 01:26.610
Thank you, Teacher.

01:27.400 --> 01:28.000
Professor.

01:28.000 --> 01:29.080
Let me see.

01:30.440 --> 01:31.370
This one of yours

01:32.160 --> 01:33.039
doesn't pass.

01:35.320 --> 01:36.240
May I know why?

01:38.160 --> 01:39.640
Look for yourself.

01:40.320 --> 01:42.180
Yuan blue-and-white porcelain.

01:52.640 --> 01:53.280
Mr. Yue.

01:57.600 --> 01:58.200
Mr. Yue.

01:58.880 --> 02:00.680
Can you stop talking in riddles?

02:00.840 --> 02:02.970
Just tell me directly what I did wrong.

02:03.600 --> 02:04.400
Xu Xiao.

02:05.640 --> 02:07.440
Have I ever talked in riddles with you?

02:07.440 --> 02:08.880
I told you a long time ago.

02:09.400 --> 02:10.530
Someone's research

02:10.680 --> 02:12.840
on blue-and-white porcelain is better

02:12.840 --> 02:14.040
and deeper than mine.

02:14.440 --> 02:17.320
I even took you to the antique market.

02:17.720 --> 02:19.240
Why didn't you go see him?

02:21.000 --> 02:21.920
Oh, you.

02:28.240 --> 02:30.600
Come, have some tea, our hero.

02:31.360 --> 02:32.120
Thank you.

02:34.240 --> 02:34.880
Xu.

02:36.480 --> 02:37.280
This weekend,

02:37.320 --> 02:39.960
Uncle Zhang is bringing two cups for appraisal.

02:39.960 --> 02:41.560
Could you take a look at them?

02:42.520 --> 02:43.120
Mr. Wang.

02:43.720 --> 02:46.180
I'd like to ask for two days off this weekend.

02:46.240 --> 02:46.880
Xu Xiao.

02:47.640 --> 02:49.800
Are you going back to school this weekend?

02:49.800 --> 02:51.079
I happen to want to borrow some books from the library.

02:51.079 --> 02:51.680
No.

02:52.240 --> 02:52.880
I...

02:54.360 --> 02:56.040
I made plans with Wang Lin and the guys

02:56.040 --> 02:57.500
to play ball this weekend.

02:59.640 --> 03:00.700
You all have plans.

03:02.840 --> 03:04.770
Then what should I do this weekend?

03:25.280 --> 03:26.410
Hurry up. Come here.

03:26.440 --> 03:26.840
Hurry up.

03:26.840 --> 03:27.480
Coming.

03:27.600 --> 03:28.200
Wang Lin.

03:28.360 --> 03:28.680
What?

03:28.680 --> 03:30.400
Are you going to the library this weekend

03:30.400 --> 03:32.079
to find some information on firing porcelain?

03:32.079 --> 03:32.600
I'm not going.

03:32.600 --> 03:34.160
Li Zhuoting and I are going fishing.

03:34.160 --> 03:34.600
Fishing?

03:34.600 --> 03:35.640
How old are they?

03:35.680 --> 03:36.800
Acting like old men already.

03:36.800 --> 03:38.079
Best bros for life.

03:38.200 --> 03:39.200
Wait for me.

03:40.360 --> 03:41.160
Zhao Xiaocen.

03:42.640 --> 03:43.920
Wang Lin, what's up?

03:44.280 --> 03:46.800
The material Mr. Liang asked us to find last time,

03:46.800 --> 03:48.079
you were the only one in the class who could find it.

03:48.079 --> 03:49.210
Where did you see it?

03:49.440 --> 03:51.320
I found it in the rare book room

03:51.320 --> 03:53.520
between the third and fourth floors of the library.

03:53.520 --> 03:55.120
There are many obscure unique copies.

03:55.120 --> 03:56.440
You can look it up there.

03:56.440 --> 03:58.920
Then ask me to come along next time you go to the library.

03:58.920 --> 03:59.640
Sure.

04:00.200 --> 04:00.960
Wang Lin,

04:01.320 --> 04:03.280
are you trying to get your claws

04:03.280 --> 04:04.720
on Zhao Xiaocen now?

04:05.240 --> 04:06.840
You need to watch out for him.

04:07.040 --> 04:07.960
What?

04:08.040 --> 04:09.640
Didn't Xiaocen help me sort out

04:09.640 --> 04:11.080
that huge teapot restoration problem last time?

04:11.080 --> 04:12.280
I have to show my appreciation.

04:12.280 --> 04:13.080
It's back to life! It's back to life!

04:13.080 --> 04:13.920
Come over here.

04:13.920 --> 04:14.280
Okay.

04:15.320 --> 04:17.720
Aren't you guys playing ball this weekend?

04:18.320 --> 04:19.250
I'm not playing.

04:19.279 --> 04:21.279
I'm going fishing with Li Zhuoting.

04:21.760 --> 04:22.160
This way,

04:22.160 --> 04:22.720
Zhao Xiaocen.

04:22.720 --> 04:23.800
Keep up with me.

04:23.800 --> 04:24.930
Let's eat together.

04:25.400 --> 04:26.160
Sure.

04:26.680 --> 04:29.400
I'm so hungry. Why isn't it our turn yet?

04:29.880 --> 04:32.740
There should be three or four tables left before us.

04:33.920 --> 04:34.400
Wu Jing,

04:35.080 --> 04:36.940
ever since you rejected Wang Lin,

04:37.080 --> 04:38.960
I think he's been deeply devastated.

04:38.960 --> 04:40.680
I feel quite sorry for him now.

04:40.960 --> 04:42.360
What else can I do?

04:42.520 --> 04:43.840
I don't like him.

04:44.040 --> 04:46.880
Am I supposed to take responsibility?

04:47.240 --> 04:48.600
But back in high school,

04:48.600 --> 04:50.320
who didn't want to fall in love in college?

04:50.320 --> 04:51.400
You can if you want.

04:51.680 --> 04:53.320
I'm going to wait and see.

04:54.560 --> 04:55.420
Let me tell you.

04:55.680 --> 04:56.760
If you keep waiting,

04:56.760 --> 04:58.880
the four years of college will be over.

04:58.880 --> 05:00.280
If you don't take the initiative...

05:00.280 --> 05:01.240
Otherwise,

05:01.240 --> 05:02.480
it'll just be us waiting in line,

05:02.480 --> 05:03.680
without a man to do it for us.

05:03.680 --> 05:04.480
Don't jinx it.

05:04.480 --> 05:06.140
How do we take the initiative?

05:07.120 --> 05:07.880
It's simple.

05:08.560 --> 05:09.120
For the next class,

05:09.120 --> 05:11.320
didn't Mr. Yue say we can team up freely?

05:11.320 --> 05:12.560
Pick whoever

05:13.000 --> 05:13.880
you like.

05:13.880 --> 05:14.810
I'm telling you.

05:14.920 --> 05:16.720
When two people spend enough time together,

05:16.720 --> 05:18.840
sparks will fly eventually.

05:18.840 --> 05:19.800
Take a good look.

05:19.800 --> 05:20.400
Yeah.

05:21.800 --> 05:22.840
Take Yuexin for example.

05:22.840 --> 05:23.300
Yuexin,

05:23.640 --> 05:25.480
how about you team up with Xu Xiao next class?

05:25.480 --> 05:26.140
Yeah, yeah.

05:27.040 --> 05:27.600
Xiaocen.

05:28.000 --> 05:29.330
You probably don't know

05:29.560 --> 05:31.160
about Lin Yuexin and Xu Xiao.

05:32.400 --> 05:34.000
Since you aren't in our dorm,

05:34.000 --> 05:35.159
you don't know about this.

05:35.159 --> 05:37.760
Yuexin, don't treat Xiaocen like an outsider.

05:37.760 --> 05:39.800
Everyone knows you like Xu Xiao.

05:42.960 --> 05:45.040
Xiaocen, you weren't at the military training.

05:45.040 --> 05:46.080
During the military training,

05:46.080 --> 05:47.800
the two of them took the punishment for us.

05:47.800 --> 05:49.200
Right, Xiaocen, you really don't know.

05:49.200 --> 05:51.760
Our whole dorm agreed during military training

05:51.760 --> 05:54.159
that Xu Xiao and Lin Yuexin are the perfect match.

05:54.159 --> 05:55.600
Alright, stop talking.

05:55.680 --> 05:56.840
Military training was a long time ago.

05:56.840 --> 05:59.040
Xiaocen, don't let them influence you.

06:00.280 --> 06:00.840
Xiaocen,

06:01.120 --> 06:03.380
I've been holding this in for a long time.

06:04.760 --> 06:05.440
Well...

06:06.600 --> 06:08.130
Is there something going on

06:08.800 --> 06:10.160
between you and Xu Xiao?

06:10.160 --> 06:11.920
Yeah, is there something going on?

06:11.920 --> 06:13.720
What do you mean by 'something'?

06:13.760 --> 06:15.840
You mean like 'a thing'?

06:15.840 --> 06:16.600
Yeah.

06:17.040 --> 06:17.720
No.

06:17.720 --> 06:18.560
No.

06:18.560 --> 06:19.400
Is there?

06:19.400 --> 06:20.280
We're just...

06:20.920 --> 06:21.680
Friends.

06:23.000 --> 06:23.440
Okay.

06:23.680 --> 06:24.880
Then both professionally and personally...

06:24.880 --> 06:26.200
Shouldn't you let Lin Yuexin

06:26.200 --> 06:27.330
team up with Xu Xiao?

06:27.920 --> 06:29.000
Exactly. Yes.

06:30.200 --> 06:31.400
It's settled then.

06:31.600 --> 06:33.260
You don't like Xu Xiao, do you?

06:33.320 --> 06:34.200
It's confirmed.

06:34.200 --> 06:35.680
Lin Yuexin likes Xu Xiao.

06:35.800 --> 06:36.800
You know that now.

06:36.800 --> 06:38.840
So isn't it reasonable to let them team up?

06:38.840 --> 06:39.280
Yes.

06:39.400 --> 06:39.800
Okay.

06:40.080 --> 06:41.280
It's settled then.

06:42.000 --> 06:42.860
You two team up.

06:43.440 --> 06:44.300
You two team up.

06:44.880 --> 06:46.200
Is medium table 37 here?

06:46.200 --> 06:46.880
Here.

06:46.880 --> 06:47.640
Time to eat.

06:47.800 --> 06:48.840
Let's go. I'm starving.

06:48.840 --> 06:49.840
Me too.

06:49.840 --> 06:50.480
Let's go.

07:02.400 --> 07:03.400
What are you doing?

07:03.400 --> 07:04.240
Why so sneaky?

07:04.480 --> 07:06.520
Sis, how have you been lately?

07:07.280 --> 07:08.320
Not bad.

07:08.960 --> 07:10.680
Why don't you ask me back?

07:10.920 --> 07:13.240
I'm miserable.

07:14.640 --> 07:15.960
Have you finished your homework?

07:15.960 --> 07:18.120
I can never finish it.

07:18.520 --> 07:20.680
My school stopped assigning homework,

07:20.680 --> 07:21.880
but I don't know where Aunt

07:21.880 --> 07:23.280
got all these questions.

07:23.280 --> 07:24.920
She makes me do test papers at home.

07:24.920 --> 07:26.520
Sis, do something

07:26.520 --> 07:28.680
to distract Aunt.

07:31.120 --> 07:34.000
Then I'll say I want to go shopping

07:34.040 --> 07:35.240
and ask Aunt to go with me.

07:35.240 --> 07:35.760
Sis,

07:35.880 --> 07:37.680
you really don't know how to lie.

07:37.960 --> 07:40.620
Aunt would probably see through you at a glance.

07:42.680 --> 07:44.240
I made an appointment with Wang Lin and the others

07:44.240 --> 07:45.360
to play basketball outside this weekend.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.240
I'm not playing basketball.

07:46.240 --> 07:48.240
Li Zhuoting and I are going fishing.

07:48.520 --> 07:49.200
Xing,

07:51.080 --> 07:51.960
if,

07:52.640 --> 07:53.880
I mean if,

07:55.680 --> 07:58.680
if someone lies to you,

07:58.880 --> 07:59.800
what's the reason?

07:59.800 --> 08:01.440
There are many situations.

08:01.800 --> 08:02.440
Like me,

08:02.920 --> 08:04.240
because an annoying buddy

08:04.240 --> 08:05.400
always asks me to hang out,

08:05.400 --> 08:06.200
I'll lie to him

08:06.640 --> 08:08.640
and say I have to do homework at home.

08:13.520 --> 08:14.000
Sister,

08:14.280 --> 08:15.140
Who lied to you?

08:15.320 --> 08:17.040
What blind fool tricked you?

08:17.440 --> 08:18.080
No.

08:19.640 --> 08:20.320
I know.

08:20.640 --> 08:22.520
It's the boy who walked you home the other day.

08:22.520 --> 08:23.760
I know. It's him.

08:24.560 --> 08:25.880
Don't talk nonsense.

08:26.000 --> 08:27.520
Sister, how dare you go behind Aunt's back

08:27.520 --> 08:28.580
and date secretly!

08:28.640 --> 08:29.840
If Aunt finds out about this,

08:29.840 --> 08:31.320
she'll skin you alive.

08:31.400 --> 08:32.240
Keep talking!

08:33.240 --> 08:34.840
Xiaoxing! Xiaoxing!

08:35.159 --> 08:36.080
Where are you?

08:37.080 --> 08:38.440
He's in my room.

08:38.440 --> 08:39.440
Over here, Mom!

08:40.559 --> 08:41.159
You hit me!

08:41.320 --> 08:42.080
I can't believe you hit me!

08:42.080 --> 08:43.280
Hurry out and do your homework.

08:43.280 --> 08:43.880
Got it.

08:55.040 --> 08:56.570
Is there something going on

08:57.240 --> 08:58.600
between you and Xu Xiao?

09:05.280 --> 09:06.340
I'm her classmate.

09:06.360 --> 09:07.320
My name is Xu Xiao.

09:07.320 --> 09:08.200
It's too late today,

09:08.200 --> 09:09.400
so I brought her back.

09:18.280 --> 09:20.200
How do I

09:20.800 --> 09:22.480
really feel about Xu Xiao?

09:26.160 --> 09:27.960
Keep up with Mr. Zhou, everyone.

09:28.120 --> 09:28.520
Go.

09:30.760 --> 09:31.280
Xing,

09:31.560 --> 09:32.800
you can't run around today.

09:32.800 --> 09:34.200
I am watching you today.

09:35.200 --> 09:36.930
Let's go. Keep up with Mr. Zhou.

09:37.160 --> 09:38.160
Come on, let's go.

09:40.120 --> 09:41.780
Children, you can take a look,

09:41.800 --> 09:43.040
which ones are porcelain.

09:43.040 --> 09:44.760
Xing, do you think this looks good?

09:44.760 --> 09:45.240
I won't look.

09:45.240 --> 09:46.960
Do you remember I told you

09:47.080 --> 09:48.610
what porcelain looks like?

09:48.760 --> 09:49.680
Smooth.

09:50.320 --> 09:52.360
What else does the smooth surface have?

09:52.360 --> 09:53.600
And a lid.

09:53.640 --> 09:54.640
Brother-in-Law!

09:55.080 --> 09:56.240
But some don't.

09:56.440 --> 09:57.080
Right?

10:10.640 --> 10:11.200
Sister,

10:11.360 --> 10:12.600
guess who I saw.

10:16.360 --> 10:17.040
Who?

10:38.440 --> 10:39.680
Stop following him.

10:39.680 --> 10:40.640
Come back here.

10:56.520 --> 10:58.600
He mysteriously entered a room.

10:59.400 --> 11:00.920
Sister, I'll keep an eye on him for you.

11:00.920 --> 11:02.600
I won't leave until he comes out.

11:02.600 --> 11:05.260
Xing, don't meddle in other people's business.

11:25.760 --> 11:26.200
Dad.

11:31.560 --> 11:32.280
Xiao.

11:38.240 --> 11:38.840
You.

11:42.800 --> 11:43.800
Why are you here?

11:47.000 --> 11:47.760
Come on in.

11:47.840 --> 11:48.920
Come in.

11:49.120 --> 11:49.680
Come in.

11:50.480 --> 11:51.200
Here.

11:52.360 --> 11:53.620
Here, have some water.

12:07.040 --> 12:07.680
Xiao.

12:08.240 --> 12:09.370
Why did you come here

12:09.920 --> 12:11.320
to see me today?

12:14.800 --> 12:15.560
Mr. Yue

12:16.400 --> 12:18.880
asked me to paint an imitation Yuan dynasty blue-and-white porcelain.

12:18.880 --> 12:21.080
I've tried twice but still don't get it.

12:21.240 --> 12:22.840
So I came to ask for your help.

12:27.600 --> 12:28.400
You made this.

12:31.160 --> 12:32.040
Not bad.

12:32.280 --> 12:33.540
You've improved a lot.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.360
Yue Qixin

12:36.920 --> 12:38.320
is still as harsh as ever.

12:39.520 --> 12:41.320
So what exactly is wrong with it?

12:42.680 --> 12:43.560
He asked you

12:43.920 --> 12:46.920
to replicate Yuan blue-and-white porcelain, right?

12:47.160 --> 12:47.960
Let me ask you.

12:48.520 --> 12:50.380
Dad taught you when you were a kid.

12:50.560 --> 12:53.160
What is the soul of blue-and-white porcelain?

12:55.760 --> 12:56.290
The blue.

12:56.320 --> 12:56.760
Right.

12:57.520 --> 12:59.080
It's exactly the color blue.

12:59.080 --> 13:01.080
Because different cobalt pigments

13:01.200 --> 13:03.330
have different coloring components,

13:03.440 --> 13:04.200
they produce

13:04.400 --> 13:06.600
different shades of blue.

13:06.920 --> 13:07.580
Therefore,

13:07.880 --> 13:09.320
your color is wrong.

13:11.040 --> 13:13.760
Yuan blue-and-white porcelain mainly uses

13:14.320 --> 13:16.000
imported sumali blue.

13:16.760 --> 13:18.560
And the biggest characteristic of sumali blue

13:18.560 --> 13:20.840
is its vibrant color.

13:21.160 --> 13:22.480
Overall, it

13:22.800 --> 13:24.320
gives off a bright

13:24.760 --> 13:25.480
blue tone.

13:26.040 --> 13:27.080
But look at yours.

13:28.640 --> 13:29.440
The color

13:30.040 --> 13:30.770
is a bit pale.

13:31.440 --> 13:32.800
The overall tone

13:33.320 --> 13:34.320
is rather soft.

13:34.800 --> 13:37.800
Yours actually looks more like Ming blue-and-white.

13:37.840 --> 13:38.320
Understand?

13:38.320 --> 13:39.520
Ming blue-and-white?

13:39.520 --> 13:40.760
But as for Yuan blue-and-white,

13:40.760 --> 13:41.490
the patterns

13:42.000 --> 13:43.130
are more intricate,

13:43.960 --> 13:45.690
and the composition is fuller.

13:45.880 --> 13:46.610
Understand?

13:47.360 --> 13:47.880
I see.

13:49.280 --> 13:50.210
What you have now

13:50.840 --> 13:52.200
is already very well done.

13:52.200 --> 13:53.040
Keep it up.

14:00.880 --> 14:02.010
By the way, Xiao'er,

14:02.240 --> 14:02.920
do you

14:03.280 --> 14:05.600
still remember that

14:05.800 --> 14:08.040
blue-and-white porcelain rabbit I gave you when you were little?

14:08.040 --> 14:08.680
I remember.

14:08.680 --> 14:09.480
You still keep it, right?

14:09.480 --> 14:10.340
I still have it.

14:13.040 --> 14:14.000
Back then,

14:15.600 --> 14:16.930
you were only this tall.

14:17.800 --> 14:18.860
I held you in my arms

14:20.320 --> 14:21.640
and taught you.

14:32.800 --> 14:34.060
After all these years,

14:35.080 --> 14:36.010
you've grown up.

14:37.880 --> 14:39.080
You've grown so tall.

14:42.400 --> 14:43.930
You look quite haggard too.

14:46.120 --> 14:47.360
Time is unforgiving.

14:48.000 --> 14:49.060
Dad is getting old.

14:51.560 --> 14:52.360
I hope

14:53.080 --> 14:54.140
that in the future,

14:55.080 --> 14:56.480
we will have more chances

14:57.320 --> 14:58.320
and more time

14:58.560 --> 14:59.360
to be able to

15:00.240 --> 15:01.280
meet up

15:02.360 --> 15:03.680
and get together more often.

15:03.680 --> 15:04.280
Okay?

15:07.760 --> 15:08.160
Okay.

15:13.600 --> 15:14.200
Oh, right.

15:15.360 --> 15:16.820
Let me show you something.

15:17.880 --> 15:18.400
Wait.

15:25.400 --> 15:25.760
Here.

15:26.240 --> 15:26.920
Hold it carefully.

15:26.920 --> 15:27.280
Okay.

15:27.600 --> 15:28.260
Take a look.

15:29.280 --> 15:30.080
Be careful.

15:33.600 --> 15:35.060
Take it out and have a look.

15:40.560 --> 15:41.090
How is it?

15:41.360 --> 15:43.290
The Chenghua chicken cup I bought.

15:43.440 --> 15:44.080
I plan to

15:44.080 --> 15:45.410
sell it for a good price.

15:45.680 --> 15:46.120
Fake.

15:47.800 --> 15:48.160
Wh-

15:49.040 --> 15:50.240
What do you mean fake?

15:50.480 --> 15:51.410
Obviously fake.

15:51.680 --> 15:53.480
What do you mean obviously fake?

15:53.760 --> 15:55.360
I told you when you were a kid,

15:55.600 --> 15:57.320
the pattern of this chicken cup

15:57.320 --> 15:58.880
comes from the Hen and Chicks painting.

15:58.880 --> 15:59.440
Look at the top.

15:59.440 --> 16:00.560
What's there to see?

16:00.560 --> 16:01.520
Isn't it obviously fake?

16:01.520 --> 16:02.600
What are you doing?

16:03.600 --> 16:04.800
Didn't I tell you when you were little

16:04.800 --> 16:06.680
to hold it with both hands?

16:07.000 --> 16:08.060
What are you doing?

16:08.880 --> 16:10.160
What's wrong with you?

16:13.000 --> 16:14.600
Xu Xiao, let me tell you.

16:15.800 --> 16:16.760
This appraisal skill,

16:16.760 --> 16:18.820
didn't I teach you when you were a kid?

16:19.120 --> 16:19.840
What's wrong with you?

16:19.840 --> 16:21.520
You just went to college for a few days,

16:21.520 --> 16:22.920
and you think you're someone else?

16:22.920 --> 16:24.240
Now you're teaching me?

16:24.240 --> 16:25.120
Are you saying

16:25.120 --> 16:26.520
that my judgment is worse than yours?

16:26.520 --> 16:28.040
All these years, I've been wandering

16:28.040 --> 16:29.560
around this street.

16:29.640 --> 16:30.760
Do you know how long I've searched,

16:30.760 --> 16:31.640
and how many times I've tried,

16:31.640 --> 16:33.280
just to find a treasure like this?

16:33.280 --> 16:34.840
I just want to use it today

16:35.200 --> 16:36.200
to turn my life around.

16:36.200 --> 16:36.760
I know.

16:38.600 --> 16:39.200
So?

16:39.560 --> 16:41.000
After I turn things around,

16:41.000 --> 16:41.640
we can

16:42.000 --> 16:43.800
go back to our old life.

16:43.840 --> 16:45.300
Life was so good back then.

16:45.360 --> 16:46.840
We can be together again.

16:47.120 --> 16:48.120
On this street,

16:48.120 --> 16:49.400
you're really lucky

16:50.040 --> 16:51.680
to have met me today.

16:52.240 --> 16:53.960
Look at this pattern and glaze.

16:53.960 --> 16:54.820
And this style.

16:55.160 --> 16:56.760
It's absolutely authentic.

16:57.000 --> 16:58.280
Isn't that great?

16:58.480 --> 17:00.080
I shouldn't have come to you.

17:00.960 --> 17:01.520
Xiao,

17:02.400 --> 17:03.520
Dad was just a little anxious.

17:03.520 --> 17:03.960
You.

17:03.960 --> 17:04.319
You,

17:04.319 --> 17:05.119
stop talking.

17:06.400 --> 17:07.260
Don't be angry.

17:07.960 --> 17:08.800
Xu Jinsong.

17:10.280 --> 17:11.810
You haven't changed at all.

17:46.000 --> 17:47.160
What are you doing here?

17:47.160 --> 17:48.690
Brother-in-law is inside.

17:53.560 --> 17:54.420
Did you see him?

17:57.400 --> 17:58.040
Xing.

17:58.640 --> 17:59.280
Teacher.

18:00.560 --> 18:03.200
Why didn't you say anything before going out with your sister?

18:03.200 --> 18:03.600
I...

18:03.600 --> 18:06.530
I told you not to leave the group without permission.

18:06.560 --> 18:08.290
Do you know how dangerous it is?

18:09.120 --> 18:10.180
I already told you.

18:10.320 --> 18:11.920
You must listen to my class carefully.

18:11.920 --> 18:13.580
You can't wander off anymore.

18:14.760 --> 18:15.690
Why are you here?

18:16.680 --> 18:17.080
I...

18:17.800 --> 18:18.240
I...

18:18.920 --> 18:19.840
I'm looking for

18:20.960 --> 18:21.680
Xu Xiao.

18:37.280 --> 18:38.400
Look at this glaze,

18:38.760 --> 18:40.760
the pattern, and the body.

18:41.400 --> 18:42.460
Good stuff, right?

18:42.680 --> 18:43.640
You should know

18:44.200 --> 18:45.960
how much an antique in this condition

18:45.960 --> 18:47.920
would fetch at an auction.

18:47.920 --> 18:48.600
Let me see.

18:48.960 --> 18:50.290
No passing hand to hand.

18:52.080 --> 18:52.610
Mr. Wang,

18:53.280 --> 18:54.760
I only trust you.

18:55.520 --> 18:56.440
You flatter me.

18:56.520 --> 18:57.600
My old man

18:57.760 --> 18:59.760
always buys these things behind my back.

18:59.760 --> 19:01.840
The thing is, he always mentions this friend

19:01.840 --> 19:02.760
or that friend.

19:03.520 --> 19:04.960
I'm afraid he'll get scammed.

19:04.960 --> 19:05.640
Seriously.

19:08.840 --> 19:10.100
But there's a problem.

19:10.640 --> 19:12.370
I don't know how to appraise it.

19:13.120 --> 19:14.960
Mainly, this isn't my area of expertise.

19:14.960 --> 19:16.880
My expertise is in management.

19:17.520 --> 19:18.000
No.

19:18.320 --> 19:19.760
No, no, don't worry.

19:19.760 --> 19:21.220
Our shop has an appraiser.

19:21.760 --> 19:22.200
Look.

19:22.480 --> 19:23.280
What a coincidence.

19:23.280 --> 19:24.840
Xiao Xu, come here.

19:26.120 --> 19:27.880
He is our top expert.

19:28.400 --> 19:29.040
Xiao Xu,

19:29.480 --> 19:30.160
take a look at this.

19:30.160 --> 19:32.280
They say it's an authentic

19:32.280 --> 19:35.520
imperial kiln piece from the Chenghua reign of the Ming Dynasty.

19:35.520 --> 19:36.120
It's fake.

19:36.280 --> 19:37.000
Fake?

19:37.280 --> 19:38.480
Why are you so direct?

19:38.480 --> 19:39.410
How could you...

19:39.520 --> 19:40.080
You...

19:40.680 --> 19:41.920
talk like that?

19:42.320 --> 19:43.920
Young man, watch your mouth.

19:44.200 --> 19:46.200
You just take one look and call it fake.

19:46.200 --> 19:46.840
Mr. Wang,

19:47.120 --> 19:49.560
who is this guy coming in and talking nonsense?

19:49.560 --> 19:52.000
He is a Cultural Relics Conservation major.

19:52.000 --> 19:53.320
A college student?

19:54.000 --> 19:55.040
Which university?

19:55.040 --> 19:55.680
JCU.

19:55.680 --> 19:57.520
Never mind what school he goes to.

19:57.520 --> 19:59.560
He's too young to be reliable.

20:00.280 --> 20:02.000
How many items have you appraised?

20:02.000 --> 20:03.200
You don't believe me.

20:04.200 --> 20:06.400
Put this porcelain bowl next to your ear

20:08.200 --> 20:09.200
and tap it gently.

20:12.000 --> 20:13.000
The sound is dull.

20:14.560 --> 20:15.920
Chenghua blue-and-white porcelain

20:15.920 --> 20:17.120
has a crystal-clear glaze,

20:17.120 --> 20:18.780
fine texture, and solid body.

20:19.000 --> 20:21.080
Tapping it gently produces a crisp sound.

20:21.080 --> 20:22.010
You heard it too.

20:22.200 --> 20:23.930
Yours sounds relatively dull,

20:24.240 --> 20:26.480
which means the glaze is not as fine as the authentic one.

20:26.480 --> 20:27.140
It's a fake.

20:27.880 --> 20:28.340
This...

20:28.600 --> 20:30.280
Not everyone can pick up a bargain.

20:30.280 --> 20:31.760
How is this possible?

20:35.640 --> 20:36.800
Doesn't it sound crisp?

20:36.800 --> 20:37.880
Look carefully.

20:38.280 --> 20:39.680
The characters on it say,

20:39.760 --> 20:41.800
'Made in the Chenghua reign of the Great Ming dynasty'.

20:41.800 --> 20:43.760
The certificate even has a stamp on it.

20:43.760 --> 20:45.400
We've been friends for decades.

20:45.400 --> 20:46.320
Would he lie to me?

20:46.320 --> 20:47.650
Enough. Friends again.

20:47.760 --> 20:49.160
Everyone is your friend.

20:49.560 --> 20:50.600
Where is his shop?

20:50.800 --> 20:52.060
He doesn't have a shop.

20:52.200 --> 20:53.080
He specifically collected this item

20:53.080 --> 20:55.080
for me from the countryside.

20:55.440 --> 20:56.800
He sold you a broken bowl for hundreds of thousands,

20:56.800 --> 20:58.200
and he doesn't even have a storefront?

20:58.200 --> 20:59.440
The item is right there.

20:59.440 --> 21:00.000
Dad.

21:00.520 --> 21:02.120
At your age,

21:03.080 --> 21:04.880
what are you thinking?

21:05.320 --> 21:06.440
You've been scammed your whole life,

21:06.440 --> 21:08.040
and you still want to pick up some bargains.

21:08.040 --> 21:08.440
You,

21:09.040 --> 21:09.920
call him right now.

21:09.920 --> 21:10.920
Okay, okay, okay.

21:12.280 --> 21:13.400
Why doesn't anyone believe me?

21:13.400 --> 21:14.330
This is so weird.

21:14.400 --> 21:15.480
Listen, Mr. Wang.

21:17.720 --> 21:19.780
The number you dialed is powered off.

21:22.120 --> 21:23.720
Why did it suddenly turn off?

21:24.040 --> 21:24.920
That can't be.

21:25.200 --> 21:25.880
I called yesterday.

21:25.880 --> 21:26.400
Well,

21:26.760 --> 21:27.600
scamming acquaintances.

21:27.600 --> 21:28.040
Dad.

21:30.400 --> 21:32.080
Our family's little savings,

21:32.760 --> 21:34.960
you ruined it all.

21:35.280 --> 21:35.880
No, you...

21:36.080 --> 21:37.080
Pick up bargains.

21:37.360 --> 21:39.420
I'll let you pick them up all you want.

21:49.480 --> 21:50.400
Zhang Jiatian.

21:50.920 --> 21:52.650
It doesn't have to be like this.

21:52.760 --> 21:53.800
Why bother?

21:54.480 --> 21:55.680
Stop picking them up.

21:55.680 --> 21:57.160
Stop picking them up. Get up.

21:57.160 --> 21:58.960
Stop picking them up, they're fake. Get up.

21:58.960 --> 22:00.020
What are you doing?

22:00.080 --> 22:01.520
Why bother? Get up.

22:01.520 --> 22:02.960
Don't make a fool of yourself here.

22:02.960 --> 22:03.820
Get out of here.

22:04.160 --> 22:04.800
Mr. Zhang.

22:05.200 --> 22:06.600
Take the old man to the hospital.

22:06.600 --> 22:07.800
Aren't you embarrassed? Let's go.

22:07.800 --> 22:09.280
How could you do this?

22:09.880 --> 22:11.240
What's going on?

22:12.640 --> 22:13.600
You too.

22:14.880 --> 22:15.920
I say, Xiao.

22:16.080 --> 22:17.410
Is it really necessary?

22:17.480 --> 22:20.280
What's wrong with you? Being so aggressive today.

22:22.000 --> 22:23.530
I'm really sorry, Mr. Wang.

22:24.480 --> 22:26.210
I'd like to ask for two days off.

22:27.880 --> 22:28.200
I...

22:28.880 --> 22:29.320
Sorry.

22:31.400 --> 22:32.040
Xu!

22:35.240 --> 22:35.840
Xu...

22:36.560 --> 22:36.880
I...

22:46.000 --> 22:46.880
Had a fight?

22:53.480 --> 22:54.320
Son, you're back.

22:54.320 --> 22:54.800
I'm back.

22:54.800 --> 22:56.440
Have you eaten? I'll cook noodles for you.

22:56.440 --> 22:56.920
Let me.

22:57.200 --> 22:57.800
We have rice.

22:57.800 --> 22:59.120
I'll make you some egg fried rice.

22:59.120 --> 22:59.780
No, thanks.

23:00.800 --> 23:02.130
I'll go to my room first.

23:05.880 --> 23:07.010
The kid has grown up.

23:07.640 --> 23:09.000
Give him some space.

23:14.840 --> 23:15.360
Xiao,

23:15.800 --> 23:17.000
to appraise cultural relics,

23:17.000 --> 23:19.800
there are six to see, one to hear, and seven unique tricks.

23:19.800 --> 23:22.360
Dad, what are the seven tricks?

23:22.400 --> 23:23.440
Look at the pigment.

23:23.440 --> 23:24.520
Look at the decoration.

23:24.520 --> 23:25.520
Look at the glaze.

23:25.520 --> 23:26.560
Look at the shape.

23:26.640 --> 23:28.040
Look at the inscription.

23:28.120 --> 23:29.200
Look at the craftsmanship.

23:29.200 --> 23:29.960
Listen to the sound.

23:29.960 --> 23:30.600
Dad.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.600
Can these methods really

23:32.600 --> 23:35.280
tell if it's real or fake?

23:35.360 --> 23:36.360
Well, not really.

23:36.680 --> 23:37.740
What Dad taught you

23:37.800 --> 23:39.400
are just some basic methods.

23:39.680 --> 23:42.320
Actually, during the process of appraising cultural relics,

23:42.320 --> 23:43.780
there will be many factors

23:43.960 --> 23:45.840
that can interfere with your judgment.

23:45.840 --> 23:47.760
Besides the cultural relic itself,

23:47.760 --> 23:50.760
the most important thing is whether your mind is pure.

23:51.640 --> 23:52.840
Let's put it this way.

23:52.840 --> 23:54.900
Regarding whether it's real or fake,

23:55.200 --> 23:58.080
as long as you can be responsible for yourself, that's fine.

23:58.080 --> 24:00.740
What does being responsible for yourself mean?

24:01.400 --> 24:03.460
It means being honest with yourself.

24:03.560 --> 24:04.960
Don't kid yourself.

24:07.960 --> 24:08.760
Xu Xiao.

24:09.040 --> 24:10.300
I'm sorry about today.

24:10.880 --> 24:13.800
I only went to the antique market because I was chasing Xing.

24:13.800 --> 24:15.930
I didn't mean to pry into your privacy.

24:38.640 --> 24:39.760
I didn't look in advance.

24:39.760 --> 24:41.320
I looked in advance this time.

24:41.320 --> 24:42.250
Working so hard?

24:42.520 --> 24:43.520
Okay, no problem.

24:44.920 --> 24:46.380
I used this glue last time.

24:46.800 --> 24:48.600
I feel like it's not very strong.

24:48.960 --> 24:49.840
Use a different one.

24:49.840 --> 24:50.880
Use my brand.

24:53.080 --> 24:55.340
But it's still better to use clay, right?

24:58.840 --> 24:59.600
Mr. Yue is here.

24:59.600 --> 25:00.730
The teacher is here.

25:00.760 --> 25:01.240
Quick.

25:02.240 --> 25:02.970
He's coming.

25:05.600 --> 25:06.320
Class,

25:06.960 --> 25:07.800
today

25:07.920 --> 25:10.050
we will form groups for the next round.

25:11.040 --> 25:12.280
Only you few are left.

25:12.400 --> 25:13.040
Have you decided?

25:13.040 --> 25:13.570
Teacher,

25:13.880 --> 25:15.320
I'm on Yan Xue's team.

25:15.320 --> 25:16.800
Yan Xue and Xiaoyi,

25:16.840 --> 25:18.120
okay. What about the others?

25:18.120 --> 25:19.360
Teacher, we...

25:19.760 --> 25:20.200
Okay, okay.

25:20.200 --> 25:21.660
You two are a group, right?

25:22.080 --> 25:23.560
I know, I know.

25:26.640 --> 25:27.280
Xu Xiao,

25:28.240 --> 25:29.770
who are you teaming up with?

25:31.560 --> 25:32.160
Teacher.

25:35.680 --> 25:36.040
I...

25:36.640 --> 25:38.080
I want to team up with Xu Xiao.
